1981;;Your Ticket Is No Longer Valid;;Canadian;;George Kaczender;;Richard Harris, Jennifer Dale, George Peppard, Jeanne Moreau, Winston Rekert, Alexandra Stewart;;drama;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Your_Ticket_Is_No_Longer_Valid;;A businessman (Richard Harris) has a younger girlfriend who loves him. He struggles to be able to perform in bed. He gets aroused however at the thought of his girlfriend being made love to by a handsome thief. The businessman becomes obsessed with tracking down the thief.